item.title: NRS3server help 711 revision
item.dc:creator: @Redemtion Redemtion
item.description:
@Redemtion wrote:

[quote=“Team_Rocket, post:4, topic:449941”][quote author=Redemtion link=topic=552838.msg4050939#msg4050939 date=1342500314]
it worked, what you set was the starting point for when new players join, and the respawn point for killed players. If you’re looking for teleports then go in actionButtons.java or commands.java and change ;;home or what not.
[/quote]

He never said he was looking for Teleports. If you’re having trouble with this, then I recommend you don’t use above a 562. You can of course, by all means, but it would be better to learn more first.[/quote]
But he said “How come when i set a new home starting point and compile it it doesnt work and just goes to the old point?”
which means hes only teleporting back home, so he needs to change his teleports.
